00:00:43.680 --> 00:00:46.224
Brother Hagin used to do it, and I want to say it too.

00:00:46.608 --> 00:00:48.480
We're not under the curse of the law.

00:00:48.480 --> 00:00:50.080
We are not under the curse.

00:00:51.520 --> 00:00:53.120
Jesus has set us free.

00:00:53.120 --> 00:00:57.828
For sickness, we have health; for poverty, wealth; for Christ has ransomed me.

00:00:57.828 --> 00:01:03.291
I'm not under the curse; Jesus has set us free.

00:01:03.291 --> 00:01:08.320
For sickness, I have health; for poverty, wealth; for Christ has ransomed me.

00:01:08.320 --> 00:01:08.720
Jesus!

