And it starts with the church.

00:04:31.870 --> 00:04:44.960
It starts with the preachers preaching true repentance, true salvation, and getting back to the basics, getting back to what matters, teaching the fundamentals in church again.

00:04:44.960 --> 00:04:46.834
And I believe it with all my heart.

