Maybe fall break is that time frame, and come and get refreshed.

00:06:11.383 --> 00:06:11.714
Come and get charged with the baptism of the Holy Spirit and fire.

00:06:20.390 --> 00:06:20.680
It's a time to just come and just soak it up.

00:06:20.680 --> 00:06:21.550
We're excited.

00:06:21.550 --> 00:06:23.450
I'm telling you all, we can pray.

00:06:23.450 --> 00:06:35.156
They'll be praying for the nation, praying for the elections and all kinds of things, praying for our country.

00:06:45.720 --> 00:06:46.020
And when we come together in a corporate setting, what great and mighty things we can accomplish in prayer!

00:06:46.320 --> 00:07:08.370
And I believe it's a time like never before that we need to be praying for this nation and praying for our officials, our presidential candidates, and praying for them for a move of God—for Trump, for what I saw when he fell on his knees, that he would have a radical conversion, a radical baptism of the Holy Spirit and fire, and that this nation would turn around.

00:07:10.509 --> 00:07:15.840
I'm telling you all, a lot of people say, 'Well, we don't need to pray about anything anymore because, you know, God's got this.

00:07:15.840 --> 00:07:17.829
' No, no, no, no.

00:07:17.829 --> 00:07:30.240
This is a time we intercede and pray like never before—that all hidden things be revealed, that we would expose the enemy's plots and plans, and that we put out the fires before they start.

00:07:38.548 --> 00:07:38.891
You can't just rely on 'well, I'm not going to pray anymore.

00:07:38.891 --> 00:07:41.680
' No, it's time to pray even more.

00:07:41.680 --> 00:07:46.200
When you start to see some victory is not when you let up on the devil.

00:07:46.200 --> 00:07:49.410
That's when you send in the bigger things.

00:07:49.410 --> 00:07:51.360
That's when you pray even harder.

00:07:51.360 --> 00:08:03.490
When you start to see good fruit and things start changing in the spirit realm, that's when it's time to send in the bigger guys to make sure we get bigger touchdowns.

00:08:03.900 --> 00:08:10.213
And you not only win the game, but you win by a landslide in the spirit realm.

00:08:23.190 --> 00:08:23.475
So, I believe with all my heart, it's a time like never before to send out the greater things in prayer—just praying in the spirit and seeking Him daily.

00:08:30.710 --> 00:08:30.932
So, my wife—I brought her on here today because she's going to read to you a prophetic word that was given.

00:08:42.229 --> 00:08:42.514
And I know some people may have heard this before, but it's worth repeating.

00:08:42.514 --> 00:08:43.920
It's worth reading again.

00:08:43.920 --> 00:08:49.440
Faith cometh by hearing, and hearing, and hearing, and hearing.

00:08:49.440 --> 00:08:54.857
It comes by hearing the Word of God again.

00:08:55.794 --> 00:08:59.650
And I know this isn't the Word, but this is a prophetic word.

00:09:00.070 --> 00:09:02.027
And so I believe it's good to listen to this again.

00:09:02.027 --> 00:09:03.166
Someone emailed this to us.

00:09:03.166 --> 00:09:04.766
Yes, and it blessed me.

00:09:04.766 --> 00:09:06.480
It blessed my wife.

00:09:06.480 --> 00:09:08.800
We both were like, 'Whoa!

00:09:08.800 --> 00:09:17.319
' Because there was a lot of things that we saw coming in 2015 that didn't quite manifest the way the prophetic voice is saying.

00:09:26.540 --> 00:09:26.880
And I believe this is why.

00:09:26.880 --> 00:09:30.120
But I'm telling you, it's the one last call.

00:09:32.737 --> 00:09:38.526
The time is setting on this dispensation of grace, and God is giving us one last call to bring in a harvest of souls.

00:09:38.526 --> 00:09:41.783
And I believe this is where we are.

00:09:41.783 --> 00:09:47.020
So, if you want to start reading, babe, I'll let you go.

00:09:53.110 --> 00:09:53.460
I had a vision, a prophetic experience as I was eating lunch recently.

00:09:53.460 --> 00:10:03.577
Suddenly, a portal opened in the spirit realm, and my angel said to me, "You are summoned to come to the courtroom of heaven.

00:10:03.577 --> 00:10:11.760
You are to record the case being tried now so that God's people will know the lateness of the hour.

00:10:11.760 --> 00:10:17.460
You must warn them so that the bride may awaken and take heed.

00:10:18.059 --> 00:10:18.959
The time is short.

00:10:18.959 --> 00:10:20.160
" Thank you, Father.

00:10:23.000 --> 00:10:28.613
I was escorted by two angels to a seat on the left side down front of the Supreme Courtroom.

00:10:28.613 --> 00:10:33.360
There were many hundreds of angels and saints already seated before the bench.

00:10:33.360 --> 00:10:42.347
I was surprised how much it looked like our Supreme Court room in America, except it was much larger.

00:10:46.880 --> 00:10:49.741
It looked more like a giant arena with thousands of seats ascending up as far as I could see.

00:10:49.741 --> 00:10:55.020
There were five big leather warrior-like chairs with wings on each side in the front row.

00:10:55.020 --> 00:11:04.649
They reminded me very much of the kind of chairs my father always sat in behind his desk at his law firm years ago.

00:11:04.649 --> 00:11:10.622
There were gold embossed cards on them that said 'recorder' on all five of these chairs.

00:11:10.622 --> 00:11:17.828
I must have been the first to arrive, and I was ushered into the one closest to the bench.

00:11:19.744 --> 00:11:24.852
I sat down and sunk into this really comfortable chair and was handed a pen and a small scroll.

00:11:30.530 --> 00:11:30.880
I was curious as I looked at it, for it looked really old-fashioned.

00:11:33.200 --> 00:11:38.160
The pen was a feather quill with an old-fashioned nib like a fountain pen at the bottom to write with.

00:11:44.400 --> 00:11:44.640
The pad was a scroll that was made out of parchment.

00:11:44.640 --> 00:11:51.640
It would open automatically as you wrote upon it when you got to the bottom of the page.

00:12:05.080 --> 00:12:05.340
It was kind of like an iPad that looked like a small Torah scroll at the same time.

00:12:06.639 --> 00:12:07.805
The angel showed me how it worked.

00:12:08.971 --> 00:12:10.693
It was extremely easy to hold and write on.

00:12:10.693 --> 00:12:20.280
When I would start to write, it would write whatever I thought of in perfect calligraphy script as fast as I thought it.

00:12:23.890 --> 00:12:25.211
The nib seemed to just fly over the parchment with ease in my hand.

00:12:27.591 --> 00:12:36.520
It would write whatever the angel put in my mind from what I saw and heard to record, and then it would describe perfectly any other information the Holy Spirit deemed important in an instant as it happened.

00:12:36.520 --> 00:12:39.920
It was the easiest thing I have ever written.

00:12:39.920 --> 00:12:44.739
It seemed to do all the work without my thinking or trying.

00:12:58.239 --> 00:12:58.639
I think this must have been heaven's way of court legal stenography.

00:12:58.639 --> 00:13:06.980
Most amazing of all, I was writing in Hebrew, and I hardly know the language at all.

00:13:06.980 --> 00:13:11.600
But somehow I understood and thought in fluent Hebrew during this vision.

00:13:11.920 --> 00:13:14.619
I cannot offer any explanation for this at all.

00:13:16.453 --> 00:13:22.260
The angel said, "You are one of five prophet recorders that have been summoned from the earth to chronicle and witness this trial soon to begin.

00:13:22.260 --> 00:13:28.1000
Just let the pen flow over the parchment and it will be a witness to the proceedings.

00:13:37.140 --> 00:13:37.530
Then you will sign it when it is finished and it will be added to the eternal ledger of legal proceedings.

00:13:37.530 --> 00:13:43.120
" Soon the other four recorders were seated and shown how to write as I was.

00:13:43.120 --> 00:13:50.100
I recognized one of them as a current prophet on earth.

00:13:50.100 --> 00:13:54.240
He was the only other from the western world.

00:13:54.240 --> 00:14:06.257
I cannot speak of whom it was at this time, and the other three of them were not known to me.

00:14:13.560 --> 00:14:13.900
We were all different races from different regions of the earth.

00:14:13.900 --> 00:14:21.750
One was a Chinese woman of great age who just glowed with the wisdom and love of God.

00:14:21.750 --> 00:14:27.863
We were dressed in black robes with red border sashes on the sides and the sleeves.

00:14:28.686 --> 00:14:37.600
The other prophet recorder was a lady from Africa who had a headdress that wrapped around her head which flashed rays of light whenever she moved.

00:14:53.554 --> 00:14:53.897
She spoke and wrote in French, I believe.

00:15:04.982 --> 00:15:05.257
The fifth was a man from South America.

00:15:09.920 --> 00:15:10.160
I was given a yarmulke of golden color.

00:15:10.160 --> 00:15:12.994
It had 12 ruby stones around it.

00:15:12.994 --> 00:15:17.299
God called me to wear a yarmulke whenever I minister on earth.

00:15:17.299 --> 00:15:21.457
So I wasn't surprised that I had to wear one here.

00:15:21.457 --> 00:15:34.267
When the angel put it on my head, I could feel the weight of it like it was made out of actual metal gold, even though it felt soft to the touch like silk.

00:15:34.267 --> 00:15:40.520
Everyone finally assembled and a great and beautiful angel who presided over the courtroom named Justice stood up.

00:15:40.520 --> 00:15:47.920
She seemed to tower over us and was about 20 ft tall.

00:15:47.920 --> 00:15:59.740
Then angels appeared with long trumpets on either side of the courtroom and sounded a fanfare that ended with a blast.

00:16:02.479 --> 00:16:04.834
The angel Justice then shouted with a very loud soprano voice, "All rise.

00:16:07.223 --> 00:16:16.587
The Honorable Ancient of Days, the Judge of All Creation, the King of Ages, the Most High Lord Almighty is present and presiding.

00:16:16.587 --> 00:16:20.453
" We all stood up exactly at the same time in unison.

00:16:20.453 --> 00:16:27.680
Then the most awesome sound of praise and worship filled the atmosphere as we all began to praise his glorious majesty together.

00:16:32.280 --> 00:16:34.080
I have never experienced such a sense of awe as the fear of the Lord filled the court.

00:16:35.580 --> 00:16:40.159
It was only then that I could just make out who was seated behind the holy bar.

00:16:43.885 --> 00:16:44.183
There were not nine judges but 12.

00:16:44.183 --> 00:16:53.310
God the Father sat in the middle with six of the Supreme Court judges on both sides of him.

00:16:54.960 --> 00:16:56.960
I somehow knew he was the final deciding vote in every decision.

00:16:56.960 --> 00:17:06.880
After our praises finished, the angel Justice, who I now saw was a lady and not a male angel, shouted, "Be seated.

00:17:06.880 --> 00:17:09.646
The high court is now in session.

00:17:13.211 --> 00:17:13.520
" She was standing just in front of his throne.

00:17:13.520 --> 00:17:18.857
She had a golden gavel and struck a giant crystalline base with it.

00:17:18.857 --> 00:17:28.813
There was a great thunder clap and lightning flashed out from the gavel base and flew across the room in all directions.

00:17:37.840 --> 00:17:38.126
It was only then that I could see the judges behind the bench.

00:17:38.983 --> 00:17:55.119
The only person that I could not see the face of was the Father, but I could see the throne he sat upon and the outline of his face.

00:18:03.600 --> 00:18:04.000
He seemed to be clothed in a white blinding light as well.

00:18:08.569 --> 00:18:09.778
He had a black robe on, but had every color of the rainbow flashing out of it.

00:18:09.778 --> 00:18:18.583
If he moved even slightly, lightning bolts would fly all over the room, out of his head, his hands, and his feet.

00:18:21.440 --> 00:18:31.733
The other judges to the Father's right hand were Enoch, Father Abraham, Moses the lawgiver, David the King, Elijah the prophet, and Daniel.

00:18:31.733 --> 00:18:39.360
On the Father's left hand were John the Baptist, Peter, James, John, Andrew, and Paul the Apostle.

00:18:53.940 --> 00:18:54.320
I do not know whether these were the permanent judges of the Supreme Court of Heaven or not, but those were the ones seated for this case.

00:18:54.320 --> 00:18:58.856
They were all also dressed in these black iridescent judge robes.

00:18:58.856 --> 00:19:08.400
There were stunning crowns of glory on each of their heads and they were holding gold scepters in their right hands.

00:19:08.400 --> 00:19:20.373
The Father in the middle on the throne of judgment held the biggest scepter and had many crowns suspended over his head that shot lightnings out of them in every direction.

00:19:21.973 --> 00:19:25.940
I could not look upon them or his face because it was so bright.

00:19:29.893 --> 00:19:30.151
It was like looking into the noonday sun.

00:19:30.151 --> 00:19:35.257
I was given one glimpse at him when he first came into the courtroom.

00:19:35.257 --> 00:19:45.406
There was a rainbow that would appear that encircled him above and below that I saw a few times during this vision.

00:19:57.000 --> 00:19:57.248
I could not endure looking at him for more than a split second before I had to avert my eyes, for the white blazing brightness was too intense.

00:19:57.248 --> 00:20:02.260
All the judges behind the great bar were emanating great light that was also nearly blinding.

00:20:02.260 --> 00:20:05.369
That is the closest I can describe them now.

00:20:17.822 --> 00:20:18.187
Then the case was read before all present by Lady Justice, the angel.

00:20:18.187 --> 00:20:26.050
She spoke: "This is the summary of the case brought before the Supreme Court of Heaven today.

00:20:26.050 --> 00:20:34.650
The timing of the final judgments of the day of the Lord must be decided.

00:20:48.827 --> 00:20:49.520
The accuser, Satan, is prosecuting, declaring that the time of Adam's lease is over, and he must be allowed to take ownership of the earth for a time and times and half a time as it is written in the Holy Scriptures.

00:20:49.520 --> 00:20:51.900
" That is the most amazing, babe.

00:20:51.900 --> 00:20:58.240
Representing the holy defense is the Lord Yeshua, Jesus the Messiah, the Lamb of God.

00:20:58.240 --> 00:21:08.023
At this, Yeshua himself stood up at the defense table as the advocate general of the bride of Messiah on earth.

00:21:08.023 --> 00:21:13.269
He was representing the holy saints of God still alive in their bodies on earth.

00:21:13.269 --> 00:21:20.389
When he stood up at the left table, everyone bowed and worshiped except those at the prosecution table to the right.

00:21:20.389 --> 00:21:28.229
There was a very handsome man who just sat stone-faced with several other princes at the prosecution table.

00:21:28.229 --> 00:21:29.920
They did not move.

00:21:31.570 --> 00:21:32.440
The headman sneered when they worshiped Yeshua.

00:21:32.440 --> 00:21:39.143
Representing the agenda of the fallen Lucifer, now called Satan, is the accuser, liar, and deceiver himself.

00:21:39.143 --> 00:21:39.936
Satan!

00:21:39.936 --> 00:21:44.500
At this, the handsome prince with the evil smirk stood up.

00:21:44.500 --> 00:21:45.500
No one moved.

00:21:45.500 --> 00:21:50.000
There was silence in the courtroom for about a minute.

00:21:50.000 --> 00:21:53.417
Then Lady Justice spoke again, "You may sit down now.

00:21:53.417 --> 00:21:56.480
" Finally, he did so with another sneering grunt.

00:21:56.480 --> 00:22:05.748
I marveled that he seemed human and actually very attractive to look at, although there was no heavenly light in him or around him.

00:22:10.388 --> 00:22:10.754
"The prosecution may proceed," Lady Justice proclaimed.

00:22:10.754 --> 00:22:13.109
At this, the man stood up.

00:22:21.573 --> 00:22:21.947
He was robed in a black suit that had a long cape of crimson red that followed behind him.

00:22:36.799 --> 00:22:38.017
He had gold epaulettes on his shoulders that were built into his cape.

00:22:38.017 --> 00:22:44.013
He was very articulate and extremely haughty.

00:22:44.013 --> 00:22:49.120
I got sick to my stomach as he spoke.

00:22:49.120 --> 00:22:58.360
He walked back and forth in front of the courtroom in long strides with his nose in the air.

00:22:58.360 --> 00:23:05.860
It reminded me of a painting of what Napoleon looked like, except this man was much taller than Napoleon.

00:23:05.860 --> 00:23:10.490
He began his long diatribe of accusation against fallen man.

00:23:10.490 --> 00:23:13.520
He seemed to know the Bible very well.

00:23:13.520 --> 00:23:19.520
Starting from Adam and Eve, he began accusing God of failing mankind in every generation.

